    <stitle>VT 275 Engine Service Manual - Fuel System - Assembly and Installation - Assembly of the HFCM</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc id="m6.5" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Assembly of the HFCM</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the thermo recirculating valve assembly into housing.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install heater assembly.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install drain plug assembly.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place cover plate gasket onto cover plate.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Position cover plate onto housing and thread in four screws (M5 x 23). Tighten screws to the
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_278.xml" xrefid="E30013B">Special Torque</hotlnk>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install new O-rings onto the fuel pump and lubricate with clean fuel.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install fuel pump assembly with three screws (#10 self-tapping). Tighten screws to the
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_278.xml" xrefid="E30013B" appearance="hottext">Special Torque</hotlnk>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install primary filter element.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Coat a new O-ring gasket seal with fuel and install onto primary filter cap. Thread cap into
                HFCM housing and tighten to the
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_278.xml" xrefid="E30013B" appearance="hottext">Special Torque</hotlnk>.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
